Player sheet MAP OF RINNEA How to play: ▼ Roll your base PHYS (no bonus). How much you can move will depend on your success. ▼ You can only move horizontally & vertically in any direction. Bold & @Terra "Move Left 4 Tiles!" ▼ Characters with 0 PHYS can only move one square in any direction. ▼...
17:00
Mission: Clear out Rinnea Aim: Find the keys relating to the Valentine's past in Rinnea. There are 6 keys. Each row only has one key. Game instructions: 1. You can choose to move together or solo. ▫️Moving together means someone will roll for movement, and another person will roll for the action tile. ▫️Victoria will always move 1 tile. It is possible for Victoria to sustain damage too. You may also choose to move with Victoria if you like. 2. At the start of every turn, roll your base PHYS. eg : !skill 3 ▫️Characters with zero phys will have a mercy 1 skill roll. ▫️You will be given 5 minutes to roll. If you don't reply, Terra will skip you this turn 3. Then, in the rp bold your movement and @ Terra. eg: Damien moves left 5 tiles to A5 ▫️You can only move up, down, left and right. ▫️If you hit the wall, you will move backwards. 4. You will then be prompted with an action/encounter. Roll accordingly! ▫️You'll be given an extra 5 minutes to reply to this. eg: You have encountered a unicorn. Roll lore. !skill 2 5. At the end of the 5 minute mark, Terra will reveal a map of the progress. ▫️Unexplored areas will appear black. Empty tiles where nothing happens appears in white. ▫️Discovered areas will appear on the left board. ▫️Where everyone is will appear on the right board
